name: afk
description: Set your AFK status with an optional reason.

name: clearnames
description: Clear all your name history data.

name: forcednicks
description: View all forced nicknames in this server.

name: forcenick
description: Force a nickname onto a member (stored in the database).

name: prefix
description: View the current prefix for this server.

name: prefix remove
description: Remove the custom prefix for this server (back to default).

name: prefix set
description: Set the prefix for this server.

name: antinuke admin
description: Toggle a user's AntiNuke Admin status (owner only).

name: antinuke ban
description: Prevents members from being mass banned in your server

name: antinuke kick
description: Prevents members from being mass kicked in your server

name: antinuke unwhitelist
description: Removes a user from the whitelist

name: antinuke webhooks
description: Prevents webhooks being spammed in your server

name: antinuke whitelist
description: Exempts a user from antinuke action

name: antinuke whitelisted
description: View the current antinuke whitelisted users

name: alias
description: Manage command aliases for this server.

name: alias list
description: List all aliases in this server.

name: restrictcommand
description: Restrict a command to a role or channel.

name: unrestrictcommand
description: Remove a restriction from a command (or clear all).

name: ai
description: Ask a question using the ChatGPT API

name: tiktok info
description: Get information about a TikTok video (downloads mp4).

name: jishaku
description: The Jishaku debug and diagnostic commands.

name: jishaku cancel
description: Cancels a task with the given index.

name: jishaku cat
description: Read out a file, using syntax highlighting if detected.

name: jishaku curl
description: Download and display a text file from the internet.

name: jishaku debug
description: Run a command timing execution and catching exceptions.

name: jishaku git
description: Shortcut for 'jsk sh git'. Invokes the system shell.

name: jishaku hide
description: Hides Jishaku from the help command.

name: jishaku invite
description: Retrieve the invite URL for this bot.

name: jishaku load
description: Loads or reloads the given extension names.

name: jishaku node
description: Shortcut for scaffolding and executing 'npm run'. Only exists if the executables are detected.

name: jishaku override
description: Run a command with a different user, channel, or thread, optionally bypassing checks and cooldowns.

name: jishaku permtrace
description: Calculates the source of granted or rejected permissions.

name: jishaku pip
description: Shortcut for 'jsk sh pip'. Invokes the system shell.

name: jishaku py_inspect
description: Evaluation of Python code with inspect information.

name: jishaku repeat
description: Runs a command multiple times in a row.

name: jishaku retain
description: Turn variable retention for REPL on or off.

name: jishaku rtt
description: Calculates Round-Trip Time to the API.

name: jishaku shell
description: Executes statements in the system shell.

name: jishaku show
description: Shows Jishaku in the help command.

name: jishaku source
description: Displays the source code for a command.

name: jishaku sql
description: Parent for SQL adapter related commands

name: jishaku sql execute
description: Executes a statement against the SQL database.

name: jishaku sql fetch
description: Fetch multiple rows from the SQL database.

name: jishaku sql fetchrow
description: Fetch a single row from the SQL database.

name: jishaku sql schema
description: Queries for the current schema and shows located table structures.

name: jishaku sync
description: Sync global or guild application commands to Discord.

name: jishaku tasks
description: Shows the currently running jishaku tasks.

name: jishaku voice disconnect
description: Disconnects from the voice channel in this guild, if there is one.

name: jishaku voice join
description: Joins a voice channel, or moves to it if already connected.

name: jishaku voice pause
description: Pauses a running audio source, if there is one.

name: jishaku voice play
description: Plays audio direct from a URI.

name: jishaku voice resume
description: Resumes a running audio source, if there is one.

name: jishaku voice stop
description: Stops running an audio source, if there is one.

name: jishaku voice volume
description: Adjusts the volume of an audio source if it is supported.

name: lastfm np
description: Show your current or last played track on Last.fm

name: commits
description: Show the most recent GitHub commits.

name: staffcmds
description: List all staff and developer commands you have access to

name: autorole sync
description: Syncs autoroles to all current members.

name: role
description: Add or remove a role from a user

name: role all
description: Add a role to all members in the server.

name: role color
description: Change the colour of an existing role

name: role display
description: Toggle whether a role is displayed separately (hoisted).

name: role icon
description: Change the icon of a specified role

name: role mentionable
description: Toggle whether a role can be mentioned.

name: settings logs
description: Show where different log types are sent.

name: github
description: Get information on a GitHub user

name: statistics
description: Set channels to display server statistics.

name: statistics clear
description: Remove all statistics counters for this server.

name: statistics list
description: List all counters for this server.

name: statistics remove
description: Remove a statistics counter from a channel.

name: statistics set
description: Set a channel as a stats counter.

name: customize
description: Customise Omex avatar/banner/bio for THIS server (premium only).

name: customize avatar
description: Manage the Omex avatar for this server.

name: customize avatar reset
description: Reset the Omex avatar for this server back to the global avatar

name: customize avatar set
description: Set the Omex avatar for this server (attach an image or provide a direct image URL).

name: customize banner
description: Manage the Omex banner for this server

name: customize banner reset
description: Reset the Omex banner for this server back to the global banner

name: customize banner set
description: Set the Omex banner for this server (attach an image or provide a direct image URL)

name: customize bio
description: Manage the Omex bio for this server (also stored in DB)

name: customize bio show
description: Show this server configured bio text.
